Interface PointDetector

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface PointDetector
extends Descriptor
    Interface for all intereting point detectors. Classes implementing this interface will often provide additional methods for additional information. Such information can be a radius or shape defining an interesting region surrounding an interesting point.
